OL,3,CJohnny Mercer may face jail sentence
OL,4,Cfor withholding names
OL,6,FFormer veterans' minister and Plymouth
OL,7,FMP Johnny Mercer is potentially facing
OL,8,Fa prison sentence after his
OL,9,Fapplication to withhold the names of
OL,10,Fthose who told him about alleged
OL,11,Fspecial forces murders was rejected by
OL,12,Fthe Afghanistan Inquiry's chairman.
OL,14,FSir Charles Haddon-Cave's ruling on
OL,15,FThursday 11 July quoted from the
OL,16,FBritish Army's values and standards by
OL,17,Fsaying: "Integrity requires moral
OL,18,Fcourage to do what is right, even when
OL,19,Fit may not be popular."
