OL,3,CJohnny Mercer may face jail sentence
OL,4,Cfor withholding names
OL,6,FMr Mercer repeatedly refused to hand
OL,7,Fover names of "multiple officers" who
OL,8,Ftold him about allegations of murder
OL,9,Fand a cover-up during his time as a
OL,10,Fbackbench MP while giving evidence to
OL,11,Fthe probe in February and has
OL,12,Freiterated that he intends to "keep
OL,13,F(his) word" to those who confided in
OL,14,Fhim.
OL,16,FMr Mercer claimed the ruling contained
OL,17,F"multiple inaccuracies and assertions"
OL,18,Fand said he found it "extraordinary...
OL,19,Fthat Mr Haddon-Cave considers it
OL,20,Fappropriate to repeatedly question my
OL,21,Fmoral courage and integrity in public".
