OL,3,CJohnny Mercer may face jail sentence
OL,4,Cfor withholding names
OL,6,F"I find it extraordinary, given my
OL,7,Funprecedented support to assist the
OL,8,Finquiry, including some names of those
OL,9,Fwho have given me consent, that Mr
OL,10,FHaddon-Cave considers it appropriate
OL,11,Fto repeatedly question my moral
OL,12,Fcourage and integrity in public.
OL,14,F"These unjustified and unprovoked
OL,15,Fattempts by a High Court judge to
OL,16,Fassassinate my character, without any
OL,17,Ffoundation whatsoever, crosses a line.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
