OL,3,CJohnny Mercer may face jail sentence
OL,4,Cfor withholding names
OL,6,F"From Northern Ireland to Iraq to
OL,7,FAfghanistan, the courts have
OL,8,Fconsistently mis-judged their handling
OL,9,Fof these issues, with appalling
OL,10,Fconsequences for serving personnel and
OL,11,Fveterans, usually of junior rank.
OL,13,F"I could comment on the naivete of the
OL,14,Finquiry team; or how ` despite my
OL,15,Frepeated requests for them to have the
OL,16,Fbasic courtesy to inform me privately
OL,17,Fbefore they release details of my fate
OL,18,Fto the press, I again found out my
OL,19,Ffate today from a journalist. But I
OL,20,Fwould consider that improper.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
