OL,3,CJohnny Mercer may face jail sentence
OL,4,Cfor withholding names
OL,6,F"He has since refused to disclose the
OL,7,Fnames to assist the inquiry, even
OL,8,Fthough: the inquiry was set up for the
OL,9,Fvery purpose of looking into these
OL,10,Fallegations; he says that his friends
OL,11,Fwere merely witnesses; he could pass
OL,12,Fon their names to the inquiry
OL,13,Fprivately and in strict confidence; he
OL,14,Faccepts that the inquiry protects the
OL,15,Fidentities of confidential contacts;
OL,16,Fand they have protection from risk of
OL,17,Fprosecution for breach of the Official
OL,18,FSecrets Act or failure to report
OL,19,Fmisconduct."
