OL,3,CJohnny Mercer may face jail sentence
OL,4,Cfor withholding names
OL,6,F"The chair has given Mr Mercer a
OL,7,Ffurther two weeks to comply with the
OL,8,FSection 21 notice.
OL,10,F"The chair's concluding observations
OL,11,Fwere that 'integrity requires moral
OL,12,Fcourage to do what is right, even when
OL,13,Fit may not be popular'."
OL,15,FMr Mercer now has until 25 July to
OL,16,Fhand over the names to the inquiry.
